name: firefox
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "76.0" %}

package:
  name: firefox
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/linux-x86_64/en-US/firefox-{{ version }}.tar.bz2  # [linux64]
  sha256: 57c69fca69afde25d72057e3162ac985ab1729b152ce432252777087877e4697  # [linux64]

  fn: firefox.pkg  # [osx]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/mac/en-US/Firefox%20{{ version }}.pkg  # [osx]
  sha256: b3ec76308b319c7dc660f383ccad803e365de1090c0d2858d85b29e0654f3c00  # [osx]

  fn: firefox.msi  # [win]
  url: https://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/releases/{{ version }}/win64/en-US/Firefox%20Setup%20{{ version }}.msi  # [win]
  sha256: 89bc9b35123ad4ee52fedbebbc406ce43b89d06629b9591d1799b9808c3abde1  # [win]

build:
  number: 0
  binary_relocation:
    - bin/firefox

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}

test:
  requires:
    - selenium
    - geckodriver

about:
  home: https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/releases
  license: MPL-2.0
  license_family: MOZILLA
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Firefox web browser

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - birdsarah
    - ocefpaf
    - bollwyvl
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
3.7.0
